quran[128]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,‘ETA ‘EMRU ELLAHI FELA TESTA’XHILUHU SUBHANEHU WE TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  16,2,JUNEZZILUL-MELA’IKETE BIR-RUHI MIN ‘EMRIHI ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U MIN ‘IBADIHI ‘EN ‘ENDHIRU ‘ENNEHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA ‘ENA FE ETTEKUNI
  16,3,HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI TA’ALA ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  16,4,HALEKAL-’INSANE MIN NUTFETIN FE’IDHA HUWE HASIMUN MUBINUN
  16,5,WEL-’EN’AME HALEKAHA LEKUM FIHA DIF’UN WE MENAFI’U WE MINHA TE’KULUNE
  16,6,WE LEKUM FIHA XHEMALUN HINE TURIHUNE WE HINE TESREHUNE
  16,7,WE TEHMILU ‘ETHKALEKUM ‘ILA BELEDIN LEM TEKUNU BALIGIHI ‘ILLA BISHIKKIL-’ENFUSI ‘INNE REBBEKUM LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  16,8,WEL-HAJLE WEL-BIGALE WEL-HEMIRE LITERKEBUHA WE ZINETEN WE JEHLUKU MA LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,9,WE ‘ALA ELLAHI KASDU ES-SEBILI WE MINHA XHA’IRUN WE LEW SHA’E LEHEDAKUM ‘EXHMA’INE
  16,10,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN LEKUM MINHU SHERABUN WE MINHU SHEXHERUN FIHI TUSIMUNE
  16,11,JUNBITU LEKUM BIHI EZ-ZER’A WE EZ-ZEJTUNE WE EN-NEHILE WEL-’A’NABE WE MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,12,WE SEHHARE LEKUMUL-LEJLE WE EN-NEHARE WE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE WE EN-NUXHUMU MUSEHHARATUN BI’EMRIHI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  16,13,WE MA DHERE’E LEKUM FIL-’ERDI MUHTELIFÆN ‘ELWANUHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JEDHDHEKKERUNE
  16,14,WE HUWEL-LEDHI SEHHAREL-BEHRE LITE’KULU MINHU LEHMÆN TERIJÆN WE TESTEHRIXHU MINHU HILJETEN TELBESUNEHA WE TERAL-FULKE MEWAHIRE FIHI WE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  16,15,WE ‘ELKA FIL-’ERDI REWASIJE ‘EN TEMIDE BIKUM WE ‘ENHARÆN WE SUBULÆN LLE’ALLEKUM TEHTEDUNE
  16,16,WE ‘ALAMATIN WE BIN-NEXHMI HUM JEHTEDUNE
  16,17,‘EFEMEN JEHLUKU KEMEN LA JEHLUKU ‘EFELA TEDHEKKERUNE
  16,18,WE ‘IN TA’UDDU NI’METEL-LAHI LA TUHSUHA ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,19,WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA TUSIRRUNE WE MA TU’LINUNE
  16,20,WEL-LEDHINE JED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI LA JEHLUKUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE HUM JUHLEKUNE
  16,21,‘EMWATUN GAJRU ‘EHJA’IN WE MA JESH’URUNE ‘EJJANE JUB’ATHUNE
  16,22,‘ILEHUKUM ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FE-EL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI KULUBUHUM MUNKIRETUN WE HUM MUSTEKBIRUNE
  16,23,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEL-LAHE JA’LEMU MA JUSIRRUNE WE MA JU’LINUNE ‘INNEHU LA JUHIBBUL-MUSTEKBIRINE
  16,24,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM MADHA ‘ENZELE REBBUKUM KALU ‘ESATIRUL-’EWWELINE
  16,25,LIJEHMILU ‘EWZAREHUM KAMILETEN JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE MIN ‘EWZARIL-LEDHINE JUDILLUNEHUM BIGAJRI ‘ILMIN ‘ELA SA’E MA JEZIRUNE
  16,26,KAD MEKEREL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FE’ETALLAHU BUNJANEHUM MINEL-KAWA’IDI FEHARRE ‘ALEJHIMU ES-SEKFU MIN FEWKIHIM WE ‘ETAHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  16,27,THUMME JEWMEL-KIJAMETI JUHZIHIM WE JEKULU ‘EJNE SHUREKA’IJEL-LEDHINE KUNTUM TUSHAKKUNE FIHIM KALEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME ‘INNEL-HIZJEL-JEWME WE ES-SU’E ‘ALEL-KAFIRINE
  16,28,EL-LEDHINE TETEWEFFAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU DHALIMI ‘ENFUSIHIM FE’ELKAW ES-SELEME MA KUNNA NA’MELU MIN SU’IN BELA ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,29,FADHULU ‘EBWABE XHEHENNEME HALIDINE FIHA FELEBI’SE METHWAL-MUTEKEBBIRINE
  16,30,WE KILE LILLEDHINE ETTEKAW MADHA ‘ENZELE REBBUKUM KALU HAJRÆN LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU FI HEDHIHI ED-DUNJA HESENETUN WE LEDARUL-’AHIRETI HAJRUN WE LENI’ME DARUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,31,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU LEHUM FIHA MA JESHA’UNE KEDHALIKE JEXHZI ELLAHUL-MUTTEKINE
  16,32,EL-LEDHINE TETEWEFFAHUMUL-MELA’IKETU TEJJIBINE JEKULUNE SELAMUN ‘ALEJKUMU EDHULUL-XHENNETE BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,33,HEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA ‘EN TE’TIJEHUMUL-MELA’IKETU ‘EW JE’TIJE ‘EMRU RABBIKE KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE MA DHELEMEHUMU ELLAHU WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  16,34,FE’ESABEHUM SEJJI’ATU MA ‘AMILU WE HAKA BIHIM MA KANU BIHI JESTEHZI’UN
  16,35,WE KALEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU LEW SHA’EL-LAHU MA ‘ABEDNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN NEHNU WE LA ‘ABA’UUNA WE LA HERREMNA MIN DUNIHI MIN SHEJ’IN KEDHALIKE FE’ALEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM FEHEL ‘ALA ER-RUSULI ‘ILLAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,36,WE LEKAD BE’ATHNA FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN RESULÆN ‘ENI EU’BUDU ELLAHE WE EXHTENIBUT-TAGUTE FEMINHUM MEN HEDALLAHU WE MINHUM MEN HEKKAT ‘ALEJHI ED-DELALETU FESIRU FIL-’ERDI FANDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  16,37,‘IN TEHRIS ‘ALA HUDAHUM FE’INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDI MEN JUDILLU WE MA LEHUM MIN NASIRINE
  16,38,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LA JEB’ATHU ELLAHU MEN JEMUTU BELA WA’DÆN ‘ALEJHI HEKKÆN WE LEKINNE ‘EKTHERE EN-NASI LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,39,LIJUBEJJINE LEHUMUL-LEDHI JEHTELIFUNE FIHI WE LIJA’LEMEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEHUM KANU KADHIBINE
  16,40,‘INNEMA KAWLUNA LISHEJ’IN ‘IDHA ‘EREDNAHU ‘EN NEKULE LEHU KUN FEJEKUNU
  16,41,WEL-LEDHINE HAXHERU FI ELLAHI MIN BA’DI MA DHULIMU LENUBEWWI’ENNEHUM FI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE LE’EXHRUL-’AHIRETI ‘EKBERU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  16,42,EL-LEDHINE SEBERU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  16,43,WE MA ‘ERSELNA MIN KABLIKE ‘ILLA RIXHALÆN NUHI ‘ILEJHIM FAS’ELU ‘EHLE EDH-DHIKRI ‘IN KUNTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,44,BIL-BEJJINATI WE EZ-ZUBURI WE ‘ENZELNA ‘ILEJKE EDH-DHIKRE LITUBEJJINE LILNNASI MA NUZZILE ‘ILEJHIM WE LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,45,‘EFE’EMINEL-LEDHINE MEKERU ES-SEJJI’ATI ‘EN JEHSIFEL-LAHU BIHIMUL-’ERDE ‘EW JE’TIJEHUMUL-’ADHABU MIN HEJTHU LA JESH’URUNE
  16,46,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM FI TEKALLUBIHIM FEMA HUM BIMU’XHIZINE
  16,47,‘EW JE’HUDHEHUM ‘ALA TEHAWWUFIN FE’INNE REBBEKUM LERE’UFUN REHIMUN
  16,48,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ILA MA HALEKAL-LAHU MIN SHEJ’IN JETEFEJJE’U DHILALUHU ‘ANIL-JEMINI WE ESH-SHEMA’ILI SUXHXHEDÆN LILLAHI WE HUM DAHIRUNE
  16,49,WE LILLEHI JESXHUDU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI MIN DABBETIN WEL-MELA’IKETU WE HUM LA JESTEKBIRUNE
  16,50,JEHAFUNE REBBEHUM MIN FEWKIHIM WE JEF’ALUNE MA JU’UMERUNE
  16,51,WE KALEL-LAHU LA TETTEHIDHU ‘ILEHEJNI ETHNEJNI ‘INNEMA HUWE ‘ILEHUN WAHIDUN FE’IJAJE FARHEBUNI
  16,52,WE LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE LEHU ED-DINU WE ESIBÆN ‘EFEGAJREL-LAHI TETTEKUNE
  16,53,WE MA BIKUM MIN NI’METIN FEMINEL-LAHI THUMME ‘IDHA MESSEKUMU ED-DURRU FE’ILEJHI TEXH’ERUNE
  16,54,THUMME ‘IDHA KESHEFE ED-DURRE ‘ANKUM ‘IDHA FERIKUN MINKUM BIREBBIHIM JUSHRIKUNE
  16,55,LIJEKFURU BIMA ‘ATEJNAHUM FETEMETTA’U FESEWFE TA’LEMUNE
  16,56,WE JEXH’ALUNE LIMA LA JA’LEMUNE NESIBÆN MIMMA REZEKNAHUM TE-ELLAHI LETUS’ELUNNE ‘AMMA KUNTUM TEFTERUNE
  16,57,WE JEXH’ALUNE LILLAHIL-BENATI SUBHANEHU WE LEHUM MA JESHTEHUNE
  16,58,WE ‘IDHA BUSHSHIRE ‘EHEDUHUM BIL-’UNTHA DHELLE WEXHHUHU MUSWEDDÆN WE HUWE KEDHIMUN
  16,59,JETEWARA MINEL-KAWMI MIN SU’I MA BUSHSHIRE BIHI ‘EJUMSIKUHU ‘ALA HUNIN ‘EM JEDUSSUHU FIT-TURABI ‘ELA SA’E MA JEHKUMUNE
  16,60,LILLEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BIL-’AHIRETI METHELU ES-SEW’I WE LILLEHIL-METHELUL-’A’LA WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  16,61,WE LEW JU’UAHIDHU ELLAHU EN-NASE BIDHULMIHIM MA TEREKE ‘ALEJHA MIN DABBETIN WE LEKIN JU’UEHHIRUHUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM LA JESTE’HIRUNE SA’ATEN WE LA JESTEKDIMUNE
  16,62,WE JEXH’ALUNE LILLAHI MA JEKREHUNE WE TESIFU ‘ELSINETUHUMUL-KEDHIBE ‘ENNE LEHUMUL-HUSNA LA XHEREME ‘ENNE LEHUMU EN-NARE WE ‘ENNEHUM MUFRETUNE
  16,63,TE-ELLAHI LEKAD ‘ERSELNA ‘ILA ‘UMEMIN MIN KABLIKE FEZEJJENE LEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU ‘A’MALEHUM FEHUWE WELIJUHUMUL-JEWME WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,64,WE MA ‘ENZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE ‘ILLA LITUBEJJINE LEHUMUL-LEDHI EHTELEFU FIHI WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  16,65,WEL-LAHU ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHJA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JESMA’UNE
  16,66,WE ‘INNE LEKUM FIL-’EN’AM LA’IBRETEN NUSKIKUM MIMMA FI BUTUNIHI MIN BEJNI FERTHIN WE DEMIN LEBENÆN HALISÆN SA’IGÆN LILSHSHARIBINE
  16,67,WE MIN THEMERATI EN-NEHILI WEL-’A’NABI TETTEHIDHUNE MINHU SEKERÆN WE RIZKÆN HESENÆN ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JA’KILUNE
  16,68,WE ‘EWHA REBBUKE ‘ILA EN-NEHLI ‘ENI ETTEHIDHI MINEL-XHIBALI BUJUTÆN WE MINE ESH-SHEXHERI WE MIMMA JA’RISHUNE
  16,69,THUMME KULI MIN KULLI ETH-THEMERATI FASLUKI SUBULE RABBIKI DHULULÆN JEHRUXHU MIN BUTUNIHA SHERABUN MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHU FIHI SHIFA’UN LILNNASI ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJETEN LIKAWMIN JETEFEKKERUNE
  16,70,WEL-LAHU HALEKAKUM THUMME JETEWEFFAKUM WE MINKUM MEN JUREDDU ‘ILA ‘ERDHELIL-’UMURI LIKEJ LA JA’LEME BA’DE ‘ILMIN SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN KADIRUN
  16,71,WEL-LAHU FEDDELE BA’DEKUM ‘ALA BA’DIN FI ER-RIZKI FEMAL-LEDHINE FUDDILU BIRADDI RIZKIHIM ‘ALA MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUHUM FEHUM FIHI SEWA’UN ‘EFEBINI’METI ELLAHI JEXHHEDUNE
  16,72,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN ‘ENFUSIKUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN ‘EZWAXHIKUM BENINE WE HEFEDETEN WE REZEKAKUM MINET-TEJJIBATI ‘EFEBIALBATILI JU’UMINUNE WE BINI’METI ELLAHI HUM JEKFURUNE
  16,73,WE JA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI MA LA JEMLIKU LEHUM RIZKÆN MINE ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JESTETI’UNE
  16,74,FELA TEDRIBU LILLAHIL-’EMTHALE ‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU WE ‘ENTUM LA TA’LEMUNE
  16,75,DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN ‘ABDÆN MEMLUKÆN LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE MEN REZEKNAHU MINNA RIZKÆN HESENÆN FEHUWE JUNFIKU MINHU SIRRÆN WE XHEHRÆN HEL JESTEWUNEL-HEMDU LILLAHI BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,76,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN REXHULEJNI ‘EHEDUHUMA ‘EBKEMU LA JEKDIRU ‘ALA SHEJ’IN WE HUWE KELLUN ‘ALA MEWLAHU ‘EJNEMA JUWEXHXHHHHU LA JE’TI BIHAJRIN HEL JESTEWI HUWE WE MEN JE’MURU BIL-’ADLI WE HUWE ‘ALA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  16,77,WE LILLEHI GAJBU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE MA ‘EMRU ES-SA’ATI ‘ILLA KELEMHIL-BESERI ‘EW HUWE ‘EKREBU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  16,78,WEL-LAHU ‘EHREXHEKUM MIN BUTUNI ‘UMMEHATIKUM LA TA’LEMUNE SHEJ’ÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUMU ES-SEM’A WEL-’EBSARE WEL-’EF’IDETE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  16,79,‘ELEM JEREW ‘ILAT-TEJRI MUSEHHARATIN FI XHEWWI ES-SEMA’I MA JUMSIKUHUNNE ‘ILLALLAHU ‘INNE FI DHALIKE LE’AJATIN LIKAWMIN JU’UMINUNE
  16,80,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN BUJUTIKUM SEKENÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MIN XHULUDIL-’EN’AMI BUJUTÆN TESTEHIFFUNEHA JEWME DHA’NIKUM WE JEWME ‘IKAMETIKUM WE MIN ‘ESWAFIHA WE ‘EWBARIHA WE ‘ESH’ARIHA ‘ETHATHÆN WE META’ÆN ‘ILA HININ
  16,81,WEL-LAHU XHE’ALE LEKUM MIMMA HALEKA DHILALÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM MINEL-XHIBALI ‘EKNANÆN WE XHE’ALE LEKUM SERABILE TEKIKUMUL-HERRE WE SERABILE TEKIKUM BE’SEKUM KEDHALIKE JUTIMMU NI’METEHU ‘ALEJKUM LE’ALLEKUM TUSLIMUNE
  16,82,FE’IN TEWELLEW FE’INNEMA ‘ALEJKEL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  16,83,JA’RIFUNE NI’METEL-LAHI THUMME JUNKIRUNEHA WE ‘EKTHERUHUMUL-KAFIRUNE
  16,84,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU MIN KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN THUMME LA JU’UDHENU LILLEDHINE KEFERU WE LA HUM JUSTA’TEBUNE
  16,85,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE DHELEMUL-’ADHABE FELA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUM WE LA HUM JUNDHERUNE
  16,86,WE ‘IDHA RE’AL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU SHUREKA’EHUM KALU REBBENA HA’UULA’ SHUREKA’UUNAL-LEDHINE KUNNA NED’U MIN DUNIKE FE’ELKAW ‘ILEJHIMUL-KAWLE ‘INNEKUM LEKADHIBUNE
  16,87,WE ‘ELKAW ‘ILA ELLAHI JEWME’IDHIN ES-SELEME WE DELLE ‘ANHUM MA KANU JEFTERUNE
  16,88,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE SEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ZIDNAHUM ‘ADHABÆN FEWKAL-’ADHABI BIMA KANU JUFSIDUNE
  16,89,WE JEWME NEB’ATHU FI KULLI ‘UMMETIN SHEHIDÆN ‘ALEJHIM MIN ‘ENFUSIHIM WE XHI’NA BIKE SHEHIDÆN ‘ALA HA’UULA’ WE NEZZELNA ‘ALEJKEL-KITABE TIBJANÆN LIKULLI SHEJ’IN WE HUDEN WE REHMETEN WE BUSHRA LILMUSLIMINE
  16,90,‘INNALL-LLAHE JE’MURU BIL-’ADLI WEL-’IHSANI WE ‘ITA’I DHIL-KURBA WE JENHA ‘ANIL-FEHSHA’I WEL-MUNKERI WEL-BEGJI JA’IDHUKUM LE’ALLEKUM TEDHEKKERUNE
  16,91,WE ‘EWFU BI’AHDI ELLAHI ‘IDHA ‘AHEDTUM WE LA TENKUDUL-’EJMANE BA’DE TEWKIDIHA WE KAD XHE’ALTUMU ELLAHE ‘ALEJKUM KEFILÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE JA’LEMU MA TEF’ALUNE
  16,92,WE LA TEKUNU KALLETI NEKADET GAZLEHA MIN BA’DI KUWETIN ‘ENKATHÆN TETTEHIDHUNE ‘EJMANEKUM DEHALÆN BEJNEKUM ‘EN TEKUNE ‘UMMETUN HIJE ‘ERBA MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘INNEMA JEBLUKUMU ELLAHU BIHI WE LEJUBEJJINENNE LEKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI MA KUNTUM FIHI TEHTELIFUNE
  16,93,WE LEW SHA’EL-LAHU LEXHE’ALEKUM ‘UMMETEN WAHIDETEN WE LEKIN JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U WE LETUS’ELUNNE ‘AMMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  16,94,WE LA TETTEHIDHU ‘EJMANEKUM DEHALÆN BEJNEKUM FETEZILLE KADEMUN BA’DE THUBUTIHA WE TEDHUKU ES-SU’E BIMA SEDEDTUM ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI WE LEKUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  16,95,WE LA TESHTERU BI’AHDI ELLAHI THEMENÆN KALILÆN ‘INNEMA ‘INDEL-LAHI HUWE HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  16,96,MA ‘INDEKUM JENFEDU WE MA ‘INDEL-LAHI BAKIN WE LENEXHZIJENNEL-LEDHINE SEBERU ‘EXHREHUM BI’EHSENI MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  16,97,MEN ‘AMILE SALIHÆN MIN DHEKERIN ‘EW ‘UNTHA WE HUWE MU’UMINUN FELENUHJIJENNEHU HEJÆTEN TEJJIBETEN WE LENEXHZIJENNEHUM ‘EXHREHUM BI’EHSENI MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  16,98,FE’IDHA KARE’TEL-KUR’ANE FASTA’IDH BILLAHI MINE ESH-SHEJTANI ER-REXHIMI
  16,99,‘INNEHU LEJSE LEHU SULTANUN ‘ALEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘ALA RABBIHIM JETEWEKKELUNE
  16,100,‘INNEMA SULTANUHU ‘ALEL-LEDHINE JETEWELLEWNEHU WEL-LEDHINE HUM BIHI MUSHRIKUNE
  16,101,WE ‘IDHA BEDDELNA ‘AJETEN MEKANE ‘AJETIN WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA JUNEZZILU KALU ‘INNEMA ‘ENTE MUFTERIN BEL ‘EKTHERUHUM LA JA’LEMUNE
  16,102,KUL NEZZELEHU RUHUL-KUDUSI MIN RABBIKE BIL-HEKKI LIJUTHEBBITEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE HUDEN WE BUSHRA LILMUSLIMINE
  16,103,WE LEKAD NA’LEMU ‘ENNEHUM JEKULUNE ‘INNEMA JU’ALLIMUHU BESHERUN LISANUL-LEDHI JULHIDUNE ‘ILEJHI ‘A’XHEMIJUN WE HEDHA LISANUN ‘AREBIJUN MUBINUN
  16,104,‘INNEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI LA JEHDIHIMU ELLAHU WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,105,‘INNEMA JEFTERIL-KEDHIBEL-LEDHINE LA JU’UMINUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-KADHIBUNE
  16,106,MEN KEFERE BILLAHI MIN BA’DI ‘IMANIHI ‘ILLA MEN ‘UKRIHE WE KALBUHU MUTME’INNUN BIL-’IMANI WE LEKIN MEN SHEREHE BIL-KUFRI SEDRÆN FE’ALEJHIM GADEBUN MINEL-LAHI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  16,107,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUMU ESTEHEBBUL-HEJÆTE ED-DUNJA ‘ALEL-’AHIRETI WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWMEL-KAFIRINE
  16,108,‘ULA’IKEL-LEDHINE TEBE’ALLAHU ‘ALA KULUBIHIM WE SEM’IHIM WE ‘EBSARIHIM WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-GAFILUNE
  16,109,LA XHEREME ‘ENNEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  16,110,THUMME ‘INNE REBBEKE LILLEDHINE HAXHERU MIN BA’DI MA FUTINU THUMME XHAHEDU WE SEBERU ‘INNE REBBEKE MIN BA’DIHA LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,111,JEWME TE’TI KULLU NEFSIN TUXHADILU ‘AN NEFSIHA WE TUWEFFA KULLU NEFSIN MA ‘AMILET WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  16,112,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN KARJETEN KANET ‘AMINETEN MUTME’INNETEN JE’TIHA RIZKUHA REGADÆN MIN KULLI MEKANIN FEKEFERET BI’EN’UMI ELLAHI FE’EDHAKAHALLAHU LIBASEL-XHU’I WEL-HAWFI BIMA KANU JESNA’UNE
  16,113,WE LEKAD XHA’EHUM RESULUN MINHUM FEKEDHDHEBUHU FE’EHADHEHUMUL-’ADHABU WE HUM DHALIMUNE
  16,114,FEKULU MIMMA REZEKAKUMU ELLAHU HELALÆN TEJJIBÆN WE ESHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘IN KUNTUM ‘IJAHU TA’BUDUNE
  16,115,‘INNEMA HERREME ‘ALEJKUMUL-MEJTETE WE ED-DEME WE LEHMEL-HINZIRI WE MA ‘UHILLE LIGAJRI ELLAHI BIHI FEMENI EDTURRE GAJRE BAGIN WE LA ‘ADIN FE’INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,116,WE LA TEKULU LIMA TESIFU ‘ELSINETUKUMUL-KEDHIBE HADHA HELALUN WE HEDHA HERAMUN LITEFTERU ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE ‘INNEL-LEDHINE JEFTERUNE ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE LA JUFLIHUNE
  16,117,META’UN KALILUN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  16,118,WE ‘ALEL-LEDHINE HADU HERREMNA MA KASESNA ‘ALEJKE MIN KABLU WE MA DHELEMNAHUM WE LEKIN KANU ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  16,119,THUMME ‘INNE REBBEKE LILLEDHINE ‘AMILU ES-SU’E BIXHEHALETIN THUMME TABU MIN BA’DI DHALIKE WE ‘ESLEHU ‘INNE REBBEKE MIN BA’DIHA LEGAFURUN REHIMUN
  16,120,‘INNE ‘IBRAHIME KANE ‘UMMETEN KANITÆN LILLAHI HENIFÆN WE LEM JEKU MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  16,121,SHAKIRÆN LI’N’UMIHI EXHTEBAHU WE HEDAHU ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIM
  16,122,WE ‘ATEJNAHU FI ED-DUNJA HESENETEN WE ‘INNEHU FIL-’AHIRETI LEMINE ES-SALIHINE
  16,123,THUMME ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE ‘ENI ETTEBI’ MILLETE ‘IBRAHIME HENIFÆN WE MA KANE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  16,124,‘INNEMA XHU’ILE ES-SEBTU ‘ALEL-LEDHINE EHTELEFU FIHI WE ‘INNE REBBEKE LEJEHKUMU BEJNEHUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FIMA KANU FIHI JEHTELIFUNE
  16,125,ED’U ‘ILA SEBILI RABBIKE BIL-HIKMETI WEL-MEW’IDHETIL-HESENETI WE XHADILHUM BI-ETI HIJE ‘EHSENU ‘INNE REBBEKE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIMEN DELLE ‘AN SEBILIHI WE HUWE ‘A’LEMU BIL-MUHTEDINE
  16,126,WE ‘IN ‘AKABTUM FA’AKIBU BIMITHLI MA ‘UKIBTUM BIHI WE LE’IN SEBERTUM LEHUWE HAJRUN LILSSABIRINE
  16,127,WE ESBIR WE MA SEBRUKE ‘ILLA BILLAHI WE LA TEHZEN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA TEKU FI DEJKIN MIMMA JEMKURUNE
  16,128,‘INNALL-LLAHE ME’AL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW WEL-LEDHINE HUM MUHSINUNE